ential steps for its objective\\\",\\n    \\\"Error-handling: includes defined procedures for detecting and reporting failures\\\",\\n    \\\"Repeatable: safe to run multiple times with consistent results\\\",\\n    \\\"Standardized-naming: follows a consistent naming convention\\\"\\n]\\n```\\n\\n---\\n# **Downstream Tasks Objectives**\\nTask task3:\\n  Objective: Format the list of subtasks as valid Python code\\n\\n---\\n# **Current Task Requirements**\\nDecompose each actionable component into specialized atomic subtasks\\n\\n---\\n\\n# **Required Output Format**\\nPython list\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"gpt_response\": \"```python\\n[\\n    \\\"Define target audience demographics (age, gender, location, income)\\\",\\n    \\\"Research target audience interests and online behavior\\\",\\n    \\\"Segment target audience into distinct personas\\\",\\n    \\\"Identify potential marketing channels (social media, email, search)\\\",\\n    \\\"Assess channel reach within target audience segments\\\",\\n    \\\"Evaluate cost-effectiveness of each marketing channel\\\",\\n    \\\"Prioritize marketing channels based on reach and cost\\\",\\n    \\\"Develop a content calendar for each channel\\\",\\n    \\\"Write ad copy variations for each channel and audience segment\\\",\\n    \\\"Design visual assets (images, videos) for each channel\\\",\\n    \\\"Format content according to each channel's specifications\\\",\\n    \\\"Implement UTM tracking codes for each campaign and channel\\\",\\n    \\\"Configure Google Analytics dashboards to monitor key metrics\\\",\\n    \\\"Set up conversion tracking goals for each channel\\\",\\n    \\\"Schedule campaign launch dates and times for each channel\\\",\\n    \\\"Configure campaign settings (budget, targeting) on each platform\\\",\\n    \\\"Activate marketing campaigns across selected channels\\\",\\n    \\\"Monitor real-time campaign performance (clicks, impressions, conversions)\\\",\\n    \\\"Track engagement rates (likes, shares, c